[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     88[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Hard constraints applied BEFORE the model scores candidates. This is both the correct security posture (opt-outs are never overridden) and the correct ML engineering (filter the action space before the policy, not after).[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     89[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The reminder ID propagation pattern (unique per-reminder ID travels through delivery receipts to enable joining events back to decisions) is correctly identified as the pivotal piece of plumbing. The sentence "If you can't join events to decisions, you can't learn" is exactly right and will save readers months of debugging.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     90[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Writing the decision record BEFORE dispatching is subtle and correct. It anchors the audit trail even if dispatch fails, and it avoids the race where an engagement event arrives before the decision is queryable.[K
